The paper deals with the problem of ranking and comparing classification algorithms in machine learning. This topic is closely related to several sub-categories of computer science, such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), software engineering (cs.SE), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). However, given that the paper focuses on the performance evaluation of machine learning algorithms, it is most likely to belong to the machine learning sub-category (cs.LG) followed by artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
